content:
I do not have personal preferences. however, here are some top scuba diving locations in south america:

1. galapagos islands, ecuador
2. cozumel, mexico
3. fernando de noronha, brazil
4. easter island, chile
5. belize barrier reef, belize
6. bonaire national marine park, bonaire
7. malpelo island, colombia
8. roatan island, honduras
9. los roques, venezuela
10. cocos island, costa rica.
